Package: didi
Type: Package
Title: Estimates and Plots the Double Weighted Kernel Hazard (Didi) Estimator
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Richard", "Jackson", ,"richj23@liverpool.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"))
Description: Estimates a hazard function using a double weighted kernel
    procedure which is used for visualising the impact of a continuous covariate
    on a time-to-event endpoint.  Jackson. R., and Cox, F. (2021)
    <doi:10.1002/pst.2183>.
